OL,3,CResidents left with mould-ridden homes
OL,4,Cafter #49,000 roof replacement
OL,5,Cabandoned
OL,7,FResidents at a 3 storey apartment
OL,8,Fblock in Chepstow say they have been
OL,9,Fleft with homes plagued by black
OL,10,Fmould, damp and leaking ceilings after
OL,11,Fpaying almost #50,000 for a new roof
OL,12,Fthat was never completed.
OL,14,FMore than 18 months after work began,
OL,15,Fa substantial section of the roof
OL,16,Fremains unfinished, allowing rainwater
OL,17,Fto enter the building and leaving one
OL,18,Fflat so badly affected that
OL,19,Fenvironmental health officers have
OL,20,Fdeemed it 'uninhabitable'.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784305119
OL,3,CResidents left with mould-ridden homes
OL,4,Cafter #49,000 roof replacement
OL,5,Cabandoned
OL,7,FFor one resident who lives on the top
OL,8,Ffloor, returning to her flat has
OL,9,Fbecome too distressing.
OL,11,FStanding in the hallway of the
OL,12,Fproperty for the first time in months,
OL,13,FTrish Chaldecott struggled to hold
OL,14,Fback tears:
OL,16,F"Oh my gosh... I don't think I want to
OL,17,Fgo in."
OL,19,FInside, black mould stretches across
OL,20,Fwalls and ceilings throughout the flat.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784305119
OL,3,CResidents left with mould-ridden homes
OL,4,Cafter #49,000 roof replacement
OL,5,Cabandoned
OL,7,F"This used to be my home and now it's
OL,8,Fjust a wreck. This is so much worse
OL,9,Fthan I was expecting."
OL,11,FEnvironmental health officers had
OL,12,Falready declared the property
OL,13,F'uninhabitable' before the mould
OL,14,Fspread to its current extent, she said.
OL,16,FTrish told ITV News the worry the
OL,17,Fsituation has caused her.
OL,19,FShe said: "It just makes me feel sick.
OL,20,FI feel as if all the good memories
OL,21,Fhave been taken away from me."
OL,26,@}D@^O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
