PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784305119
OL,3,CResidents left with mould-ridden homes
OL,4,Cafter #49,000 roof replacement
OL,5,Cabandoned
OL,7,FThe damage extends beyond Trish's home.
OL,9,FDirectly below lives 79-year-old Babs
OL,10,FJones, who says rainwater continues to
OL,11,Ffind its way into the building
OL,12,Fwhenever heavy rain falls.
OL,14,FThe pensioner says she has emptied
OL,15,F'gallons of water' from the apartments
OL,16,Fabove in an effort to prevent water
OL,17,Foverflowing into her own home and
OL,18,Ftells of the impact it's having on her:
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784305119
OL,3,CResidents left with mould-ridden homes
OL,4,Cafter #49,000 roof replacement
OL,5,Cabandoned
OL,7,F"I've not slept properly ever since
OL,8,Fthis whole business began. The mind
OL,9,Fjust goes over and over the horror
OL,10,Fstory that we're living through. I
OL,11,Fcan't go away.
OL,13,F"The things I should be doing now in
OL,14,Fpossibly my last fit years can't
OL,15,Fhappen because he's got my money", the
OL,16,F79-year-old told ITV News.
OL,18,FAn independent chartered building
OL,19,Fsurveyor, who reviewed footage from
OL,20,Finside the property, described the
OL,21,Fextent of the mould as "shocking".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
