SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784305119
OL,3,CResidents left with mould-ridden homes
OL,4,Cafter #49,000 roof replacement
OL,5,Cabandoned
OL,7,FHe warned that once moisture enters a
OL,8,Fbuilding, particularly one that is
OL,9,Funoccupied or poorly ventilated, mould
OL,10,Fcan spread rapidly.
OL,12,F"That is really extensive, chronic
OL,13,Fmould growth and very dangerous to
OL,14,Fanybody occupying that flat", he told
OL,15,FITV News.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
