SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784305119
OL,3,CResidents left with mould-ridden homes
OL,4,Cafter #49,000 roof replacement
OL,5,Cabandoned
OL,7,FResidents say they have tried
OL,8,Frepeatedly to recover their money or
OL,9,Fseek further action but have reached a
OL,10,Fdead end and they say they have
OL,11,Feffectively been left without a clear
OL,12,Froute to redress.
OL,14,FOne resident said: "We've done
OL,15,Feverything we were told to do. We
OL,16,Fcarried out checks before appointing
OL,17,Fthe contractor, we've reported what's
OL,18,Fhappened afterwards and we've followed
OL,19,Fevery avenue available to us. Yet
OL,20,Fwe're still left with an unfinished
OL,21,Froof and #49,000 gone."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784305119
OL,3,CResidents left with mould-ridden homes
OL,4,Cafter #49,000 roof replacement
OL,5,Cabandoned
OL,7,FThe Wiltshire based company employed
OL,8,Fto carry out the work was called Rise
OL,9,FAbove Roofing but according to
OL,10,FCompanies House ceased trading in June
OL,11,F2026.
OL,13,FIts owner, Robert Burton, declined ITV
OL,14,FWales' request for an interview and
OL,15,Fafter initially corresponding by
OL,16,Femail, he said he did not wish to
OL,17,Frespond to questions about the
OL,18,Fincomplete work, what happened to the
OL,19,Fmoney or whether any funds would be
OL,20,Freturned to residents.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784305119
OL,3,CResidents left with mould-ridden homes
OL,4,Cafter #49,000 roof replacement
OL,5,Cabandoned
OL,7,FHe said only that the business had
OL,8,Fexperienced difficulties because of
OL,9,Fpersonal circumstances.
OL,11,FSurveyors and roofing specialists warn
OL,12,Fthat cases involving unfinished
OL,13,Froofing projects are becoming an
OL,14,Fincreasing concern because of a
OL,15,Fshortage of skilled professionals and
OL,16,Fpoor workmanship and it can leave
OL,17,Fhomeowners facing significant repair
OL,18,Fbills long after the original
OL,19,Fcontractor has gone.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
